{"tid":1941043,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"5~6日去 三藩市 洛杉磯 唔識揸車","createTime":"2020-03-24T07:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T00:15:31.000Z","uid":5836,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9e0cbadd3a1f1148a56e604f72f2a2a745a5b9","tid":1941043,"uid":5836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"我相信應該無可能去哂兩度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扣左搭飛機有5~6日，第一次去美國揀去邊到好<br />\n唔揸車係咪好唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb1c9274bfd1935abecde3524a46c124f3dcc99","tid":1941043,"uid":218494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c9e0cbadd3a1f1148a56e604f72f2a2a745a5b9","tid":1941043,"uid":5836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"我相信應該無可能去哂兩度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扣左搭飛機有5~6日，第一次去美國揀去邊到好<br />\n唔揸車係咪好唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"f0ea25e86d510adfd91efd828d33eafc8210e79f","tid":1941043,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"坐夜巴囉,內陸機又得"},{"pid":"a4d625edfc6636ab4ed47f7eb4e34c83a3953a9a","tid":1941043,"uid":105553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0ea25e86d510adfd91efd828d33eafc8210e79f","tid":1941043,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"坐夜巴囉,內陸機又得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:34:35.000Z","msg":"依家嚟？！加州呢度而家shelter-in-place，政府叫人無必要唔好出街。餐廳知可以做外賣。"},{"pid":"047afaf4f80ed78e6a6126b853f22707671fb0f9","tid":1941043,"uid":181448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"san fran 唔渣車都冇問題，公交交通好方便，LA 就麻煩D, 但都叫有巴士既"},{"pid":"4bfb3bed64188275518d2a3982bb0bea1c6e65d2","tid":1941043,"uid":5836,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a4d625edfc6636ab4ed47f7eb4e34c83a3953a9a","tid":1941043,"uid":105553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f0ea25e86d510adfd91efd828d33eafc8210e79f","tid":1941043,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:31:57.000Z","msg":"坐夜巴囉,內陸機又得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:34:35.000Z","msg":"依家嚟？！加州呢度而家shelter-in-place，政府叫人無必要唔好出街。餐廳知可以做外賣。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:24:42.000Z","msg":"plan 緊一年後"},{"pid":"9c2475cf7ea1aaf10971c051200e76761a9f6411","tid":1941043,"uid":5836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"047afaf4f80ed78e6a6126b853f22707671fb0f9","tid":1941043,"uid":181448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"san fran 唔渣車都冇問題，公交交通好方便，LA 就麻煩D, 但都叫有巴士既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:26:16.000Z","msg":"咁你覺得可以留幾耐啊？<br />\n非深度遊亦非走馬看花<br />\n睇主要景點 食同買咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0bb9977321ba90a730bc4078a7660c1c259a35","tid":1941043,"uid":180760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"LA 我通常搭uber... LA 揸車好麻煩 🙁"},{"pid":"40d82a0bb6433f5e6e233df0d5db081e8eec208e","tid":1941043,"uid":105553,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9c2475cf7ea1aaf10971c051200e76761a9f6411","tid":1941043,"uid":5836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"047afaf4f80ed78e6a6126b853f22707671fb0f9","tid":1941043,"uid":181448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T08:16:18.000Z","msg":"san fran 唔渣車都冇問題，公交交通好方便，LA 就麻煩D, 但都叫有巴士既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T10:26:16.000Z","msg":"咁你覺得可以留幾耐啊？<br />\n非深度遊亦非走馬看花<br />\n睇主要景點 食同買咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T18:37:51.000Z","msg":"SF：<br />\n<br />\n1-2 兩日應該玩晒：<br />\n大cable car<br />\n行Union Square，買野食野。<br />\n去Lambord Street影相。依家車唔俾入，搭cable car行去。<br />\n行下Golden Gate Park（好Q大），裡面有博物館。<br />\n漁人碼頭食海鮮，Pier39睇海獅。有船去Alcatraz但好早要book飛。<br />\n行市政府附近建築物。<br />\n睇musical<br />\nChinatown<br />\nCastro<br />\n<br />\nSF 附近有車可以：<br />\nNapa有酒園同餐廳。<br />\nBrentwood果園摘生果。<br />\nMonterey睇海景。<br />\n去Stanford，Berkeley行campus，Stanford建築值得睇，教友可以去church望禮拜。<br />\nSilicon Valley去睇Computer History Museum，Google總部（只可以建築物外影相，同去gift shop），Apple 總部（same，總部Apple Store有限定貨品）Intel Museum。<br />\n<br />\nLA 睇你想玩乜：<br />\n<br />\nDisney，Universal Studios去一個都要成日。<br />\nHollywood Boulevard，Rodeo Drive名店街可以行2鐘影下相<br />\n鍾意史前動物可以去La Brea tar pit。<br />\n可以去Santa Monica行下海灘不過香港人應該唔覺太特別。<br />\nOutlet shopping可以去Desert Hills。離開LA好遠，要自己開車。<br />\n<br />\nLA好多野食，餐廳開得夜。<br />\n去Japantown食日本野。<br />\n去K-town食韓燒。"},{"pid":"3389df984f4932b596b3f1a4f7bf1c980e7ba3c3","tid":1941043,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T18:39:27.000Z","msg":"LA 揸去SF你會揸到想死, 識揸車都唔會想揸, 坐couch bus算數啦"},{"pid":"37e0e6a60a2566142b9ef660d2b91da647393937","tid":1941043,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3389df984f4932b596b3f1a4f7bf1c980e7ba3c3","tid":1941043,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T18:39:27.000Z","msg":"LA 揸去SF你會揸到想死, 識揸車都唔會想揸, 坐couch bus算數啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T18:49:21.000Z","msg":"okay啦，我中途有時停Harris Ranch食牛排。不過上面已經話唔識揸車，咁得坐巴士同內陸機。"},{"pid":"5f60dd42787ae4124c979e6aa1009569dc3bf83a","tid":1941043,"uid":144427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T18:53:25.000Z","msg":"5-6日去晒呢兩個地方點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭內陸機都好chur <br />\n巴士起碼6個鐘你冇時間<br />\nSF最少都3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLA唔識揸車一係你好有錢<br />\n一係你有好多時間搭巴士<br />\nDowntown去Santa Monica要個半鐘<br />\n你不如直接飛NY/Florida"},{"pid":"6d2e26a95cc2c78bdae9bd9c7ce8deeff1b65ee4","tid":1941043,"uid":59680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c9e0cbadd3a1f1148a56e604f72f2a2a745a5b9","tid":1941043,"uid":5836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"我相信應該無可能去哂兩度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扣左搭飛機有5~6日，第一次去美國揀去邊到好<br />\n唔揸車係咪好唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T19:07:42.000Z","msg":"唔揸車你預左會睇少啲野<br />\n<br />\n5-6日 SF + LA 點都會有少少走馬看花<br />\n因為transit都會用左唔少時間<br />\n揸車飛車都要6個鐘<br />\n咁你諗下搭夜巴要幾耐<br />\n<br />\n同埋睇下你張機票有冇open-jaw<br />\n如果SF入LA走都仲有可能<br />\n唔係既話都幾濕滯<br />\n<br />\n我嗰時時間充裕啲就揀左Amtrak火車<br />\n（美國火車出左名delay, 慎重考慮）<br />\n（由SF搭巴士落San Luis Obispo再轉火車）<br />\n（嗰時我覺得搭8個鐘巴士會死，所以先揀火車）<br />\n<br />\n巴士就可以揀Greyhound<br />\n如果你時間咁短就得呢個option <br />\n都係上網買飛啲輕鬆野<br />\n<br />\n講真<br />\n交通預鬆啲時間<br />\n嗰時就算我搭夜巴入Vegas都遲左成個鐘<br />\n車程愈長就再預鬆啲<br />\n<br />\n城市入面交通就相對輕鬆既<br />\nSF 平既就有輕鐵MUNI, 仲有一堆接駁巴士<br />\n大概$2.5可以任搭半日<br />\n地鐵就貴野黎既 $3一程<br />\n<br />\nLA就都係巴士+地鐵 為主<br />\n價錢都係可接受既 鬼叫冇車咩<br />\n<br />\n景點方面<br />\n如果主要係市區入面<br />\n2-3日一個城市都無問題既<br />\n如果想去Universal Studio/Disneyland/National Park<br />\n咁就要再諗諗<br />\n<br />\nLA 嗰時去左<br />\n-Observatory<br />\n-Little Tokyo（便當連稅都要$13）<br />\n-Chinatown (搵平野食 $5一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n-仲有嗰條好舊好短既纜車<br />\n<br />\n嗰時因為主要想入Vegas睇Grand Canyon<br />\n所以淨係俾左一日LA <br />\n你預一日就真係行得咁多<br />\n仲要唔係太深度<br />\n<br />\n大概就係咁了<br />\n嗰時大學畢業超窮遊<br />\n如果你有啲錢就可以再諗多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb71cbe9941df1a766a5d3b513a839abfc8f3f2a","tid":1941043,"uid":125515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T19:10:22.000Z","msg":"LA 唔揸車邊到都唔使去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBetween 而家全城lockdown 好多野刪門<br />\n你諗住去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b3e43e40b15fe264986fa9a4b826b5ac80d881","tid":1941043,"uid":189377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:51:58.000Z","msg":"之前一條友去LA都係搭uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac399f1a41e9e02fe62f5fb805f412b764289ca","tid":1941043,"uid":69472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"LA去k town食韓燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89921c8f97c1751adc3286f6d3080e90467ad425","tid":1941043,"uid":251852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T16:47:36.000Z","msg":"LA 叫 lyft 好多coupon, 又多車~~"},{"pid":"5fede71c6524446b1055fbd5fa8280166ca803fe","tid":1941043,"uid":75394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29b3e43e40b15fe264986fa9a4b826b5ac80d881","tid":1941043,"uid":189377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:51:58.000Z","msg":"之前一條友去LA都係搭uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:21:54.000Z","msg":"絲打住邊間酒店<br />\nUber貴唔貴"},{"pid":"5cd521e6448e1de1e18fdb1426dd53922f318825","tid":1941043,"uid":189377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fede71c6524446b1055fbd5fa8280166ca803fe","tid":1941043,"uid":75394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29b3e43e40b15fe264986fa9a4b826b5ac80d881","tid":1941043,"uid":189377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T01:51:58.000Z","msg":"之前一條友去LA都係搭uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:21:54.000Z","msg":"絲打住邊間酒店<br />\nUber貴唔貴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T01:28:06.000Z","msg":"我窮遊住hostel咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />uber睇你去邊 我down town去santa monica好似20幾蚊"},{"pid":"ba56de6391f9162701f491b6e2eb30aab69d9283","tid":1941043,"uid":5836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:25:55.000Z","msg":"咁如果去new york呢<br />\n好似方便好多"},{"pid":"ba3d09260dd8241438618e7ec9596104ae92c37a","tid":1941043,"uid":59648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba56de6391f9162701f491b6e2eb30aab69d9283","tid":1941043,"uid":5836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:25:55.000Z","msg":"咁如果去new york呢<br />\n好似方便好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T16:48:57.000Z","msg":"New york冇車嚟講交便好多<br />\n你順便可以去埋Washington睇museum<br />\n惟一唔好處係你jet lag有成12個鐘"},{"pid":"c2cf1124ac0d8e00941dd765d3f22d61a451b327","tid":1941043,"uid":114830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T17:00:24.000Z","msg":"我上年七月都去完三藩市同LA<br />\n同你差唔多，一樣唔識揸車，<br />\n三藩市同LA各去咗兩日，<br />\n中間搭內陸機由三藩市去LA<br />\n<br />\n喺三藩市我主要用Muni Day Pass同幾程uber去啲景點，<br />\nMuni day pass包咗電車，巴士同地鐵，<br />\n所以其實都幾方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺LA就主要坐Uber，<br />\n因為景點相隔太遠，兼巴士同地鐵真係太慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以俾啲uber價錢樓主參考，<br />\n喺SF由twin peaks去union square要18美金<br />\nFisherman Wharf去golden gate bridge visitor centre要11美金<br />\n<br />\n喺LA，機場酒店去Hollywood要28美金<br />\nHollywood去Griffith observatory要13美金<br />\nDowntown去getty centre要26美金<br />\nGetty去Santa Monica要16美金<br />\n<br />\n行程方面，<br />\n我自問自己係寧願chur啲走馬看花都要去多啲景點嘅人，<br />\n所以喺SF兩日同LA兩日都叫做去到啲比較重要嘅景點<br />\n<br />\n我喺SF用兩日去咗呢啲地方，<br />\n渡輪大廈, 柯伊特塔, 九曲花街, 唐人街, 聯合廣場, 市政廳, 纜車博物館, 阿拉莫廣場和彩繪女士, 雙子峰, 金門大橋觀光中心, 藝術宮, 漁人碼頭, 坐船遊san francisco bay<br />\n<br />\n喺LA就用咗2日去呢啲地方（當中有半日用咗嚟坐飛機由三藩市去LA）<br />\n荷里活, 荷里活明星住所和市內巴士觀光遊, 格里斐斯天文台, Downtown中央市場, Angels Flight, Walt Disney Concert Hall, 蓋蒂中心, 聖塔莫尼卡, 比華利山<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">如果樓主有興趣嘅話，都可以參考下我呢個trip嘅遊記嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793852\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793852</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"331bb531523c8759163caee115d17d73370240c9","tid":1941043,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T21:21:22.000Z","msg":"LA 玩槍好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有齊黑警啲槍<br />\n冇槍牌都可以玩"},{"pid":"ee0251f168e01a9a0a7d41a23be6c930bd8f5d27","tid":1941043,"uid":227452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T00:13:47.000Z","msg":"LA同SF啲住宿幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n住民宿都至少千幾二千蚊一晚 4個人<br />\n<br />\n不過夜巴都唔係話太辛苦 兩三個鐘就停一停油站 瞓下覺 睇下手機就過 可能因為後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭巴士建議flix bus或者mega bus<br />\ngreyhound之前有唔好嘅經驗<br />\n<br />\n之前SF坐巴士去LA再坐去Vegas<br />\n個人覺得LA好似多嘢睇啲 嗰陣去晒兩個theme park<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有天文台 荷里活 santa monica getty museum<br />\nkorea town啲嘢食好鬼正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSF都幾正 金門大橋下面仲有個海防古蹟 隔離有好大個公園同沙灘仔 行遠啲仲有藝術宮 幾靚<br />\nchina town啲嘢好平好多選擇 其本上香港食到嘅都有<br />\npier 39都幾好行 真係好鬼多海獅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以去食下海鮮 不過我食嗰間冇乜特別 仲要貴 真係食環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a999dd2d6ddd69bf66fa7d57c7604bfc77555d24","tid":1941043,"uid":227452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T00:15:31.000Z","msg":"LA賣嘢食個market都好鬼正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}